description: The new cases have all been linked to a resident who returned to the island from north-west England.
title: Coronavirus: Fifth case confirmed in new Isle of Man cluster
title_page: Coronavirus: Fifth case confirmed in new Isle of Man cluster - BBC News
maintext: Although the recent cases have sprung up on the island, the spread is not classed as uncontrolled community transmission as the origin of the cluster has been clearly identified.
